{"tid":1741323,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【高層執位】滙控炒房CEO傳被撤走 最快年底公佈","createTime":"2019-11-20T09:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:07:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"af1b10e0bca81640475eaf2b04e4b71f5c1006e8","tid":1741323,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"滙控（005）早前預告明年初將公布重組策略，英國《金融時報》引述消息人士指，一系列管理層變動下，執掌「炒房」近10年的環球銀行及資本市場行政總裁安思明（Samir Assaf）將被調任該部門的非執行職位（non-executive role）。報導指，有關高管變動將於今年稍後時間或明年初公布，滙控對傳聞不予置評。<br />\n安思明於2011年出任環球銀行及資本市場行政總裁，接替當時出任滙控行政總裁的歐智華（Stuart Gulliver），為其手下愛將。當年歐智華退任後，安思明更一度傳為行政總裁繼任人「跑馬仔」之列，後來雖由范寧（John Flint）跑出，惟范寧就職僅18個月便告退任。<br />\n滙控今年第3季季績遜預期，更罕有取消有形股本回報（RoTE）超過11%的目標。以往為集團盈利引擎的「炒房」的環球銀行及資本市場，經調整除稅前利潤12.41億美元，按年跌29.7%。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191120/large/1574238772_4534.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191120%2Flarge%2F1574238772_4534.png&h=bf1c4627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191120/60288796\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60288796&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=63961668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60288796&h=1854a3ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191120/60288796</a>"},{"pid":"4beace94e8a49a46f8a35a12684de35943c142e3","tid":1741323,"uid":8880,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"半年內第三個大粒嘢走 實有事發生<br />\n點解咁耐都未走漏風聲"},{"pid":"bde9f658091058cc93c2edda6947a4ef6e2f2e55","tid":1741323,"uid":70227,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:42:52.000Z","msg":"hsbc似乎會出事<br />\n大家轉定銀行"}